Peter Capaldi on next series of Doctor Who: Scary, strange, sad and funny

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Doctor Who star Peter Capaldi has taken time out from his time travels to answer some of your questions.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
